OL,3,CPitch perfect: Meet the new manager of
OL,4,CShrewsbury Town with an unexpected
OL,5,Ctalent
OL,7,FGareth Ainsworth tells ITV News
OL,8,FCentral's Sport Correspondent Dan
OL,9,FSalisbury-Jones that being a frontman
OL,10,Fin a band is just like "being a
OL,11,Ffrontman in the dugout".
OL,13,FIn Gareth Ainsworth, Shrewsbury Town
OL,14,Fhave found a man who is not your
OL,15,Ftypical football manager.
OL,17,FHe is also the lead singer of a band
OL,18,Fcalled 'The Cold Blooded Hearts' and
OL,19,Fit is that he tells me which will
OL,20,Fsuffer most from his move to
OL,21,FShropshire.
