OL,5,Ctalent
OL,7,F"Being a frontman in a band is very
OL,8,Fsimilar, you wouldn't believe to being
OL,9,Fa frontman in the dug out on the side
OL,10,Fthere. The energy you can get at a
OL,11,Fgig, it's a feeling, it's a feel-good
OL,12,Fthing."
OL,14,FIf you'd not heard of Gareth before
OL,15,Fyou might be understandably alarmed by
OL,16,Fthe club appointing a rock star but be
OL,17,Fassured Gareth is best known for his
OL,18,Fwork in sport.
