OL,3,CPitch perfect: Meet the new manager of
OL,4,CShrewsbury Town with an unexpected
OL,5,Ctalent
OL,7,FHe guided Wycombe Wanderers to the
OL,8,FChampionship, his last job was at QPR,
OL,9,Fhe kept them in the same division but
OL,10,Fwas sacked after a poor start to last
OL,11,Fseason. He says the music helps him
OL,12,Fcope with the stress of football.
OL,14,FHe said: "Football management is an
OL,15,Fincredibly stressful job. You know,
OL,16,Fyou have to be at the top of your game
OL,17,Fmy whole career and I've always had
OL,18,Fthe music on the side to go to and
OL,19,Fjust to distract me.
