OL,3,CPitch perfect: Meet the new manager of
OL,4,CShrewsbury Town with an unexpected
OL,5,Ctalent
OL,7,F"Monday evenings used to be a lot
OL,8,Fabout what chord is next or what lyric
OL,9,Fis next, never mind what team we're
OL,10,Fplaying and that might have to be put
OL,11,Faside.
OL,13,F"The band is probably the the big
OL,14,Fsufferers in me moving up to the
OL,15,FMidlands. But for me now, my music is
OL,16,Fhere, and I want to see it on the
OL,17,Fpitch from these boys."
