OL,3,CPitch perfect: Meet the new manager of
OL,4,CShrewsbury Town with an unexpected
OL,5,Ctalent
OL,7,FAt Shrewsbury Town he has a serious
OL,8,Fjob on his hands. The team are bottom
OL,9,Fof League One and facing relegation
OL,10,Funless he can turn things around.
OL,12,F"I want to see us just believing that
OL,13,Fwe can beat anybody in this league
OL,14,Fbecause it's 11 against 11. There's no
OL,15,Freason that Shrewsbury Town can't pick
OL,16,Fpoints up against anyone in League
OL,17,FOne."
